 cách bấm&nbsp;<strong>Ứng tuyển</strong>&nbsp;ngay dưới đây.</p><p>Hạn nộp hồ sơ: 12/07/2024</p><p><br></p><p>Ứng tuyển ngay</p><p><br></p>',7000000,12500000,15,0,'offline','fulltime','2024-08-18 00:00:00',2,6,'Nhân viên',NULL,79,'2024-06-18 12:41:59','2024-06-18 12:41:59'),(28,4,'Digital Business Administration - Product Owner Work Admin - Quận 11','<h3>Mô tả công việc</h3><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>We are seeking a highly organized and detail-oriented Product Owner Work Admin to join our growing team. In this role, you will play a vital part in supporting the Product Owner in managing the product backlog, facilitating product discussions, and ensuring the smooth delivery of product development.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>Product Communication and Presentations:</strong></p><p>Collaborate with the Product Owner to develop clear and concise presentations that effectively showcase product features and functionalities to stakeholders. This may involve creating visually appealing slides, infographics, and user stories.</p><p>Participate in User Acceptance Testing (UAT) sessions by preparing presentations and actively gathering user feedback. Translate this feedback into actionable insights for the Product Owner.</p><p>Work with the Product Owner to present product updates to stakeholders with clarity and enthusiasm.</p><p>Ensure product documentation is up-to-date and easily accessible for all stakeholders. This includes creating user manuals, FAQs, and other knowledge base materials.</p><p>Regularly communicate product updates and changes to stakeholders through various channels (e.g., email, internal communication platforms).</p><h3>Yêu cầu ứng viên</h3><p><strong>Administrative Support:</strong></p><p>Schedule meetings for product discussions, manage calendars for the Product Owner and stakeholders, and craft clear and concise agendas outlining key discussion points and decisions.</p><p>Take detailed and well-organized minutes during meetings, capturing key decisions, action items, and deadlines. Ensure minutes are distributed promptly to all attendees.</p><p>Organize and maintain a central repository for all product documentation. Utilize tools and best practices to ensure easy access and searchability.</p><p>Perform other administrative tasks assigned by the Product Owner to ensure the smooth operation of the product development process. This may include managing product licenses and coordinating with other stakeholders.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>Understanding of Agile and Scrum methodologies.</p><p>Excellent organizational and time management skills.</p><p>Ability to work independently and as part of a team.</p><p>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</p><p>Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite.</p><p>Ability to handle high-pressure situations.</p><p>Comfortable with using English at work, especially in writing and reading.</p><p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p><p><strong>Experience:&nbsp;</strong>Minimum of 3 years of relevant experience.</p><p><strong>Start Date:&nbsp;</strong>As soon as possible.</p><h3>Quyền lợi</h3><p><strong>Location:&nbsp;</strong>Melinh Point, No. 02 Ngo Duc Ke, Ben Nghe Ward, District 1, Ho Chi Minh</p><p><strong>Base Salary:&nbsp;</strong>up to 12,000,000 VND)&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Meal Allowance:&nbsp;</strong>500,000 VND&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Monthly KPI Incentive:&nbsp;</strong>1,200,000 VND</p><h3>Địa điểm làm việc</h3><p>- Hồ Chí Minh: The Flemington Tower - 182 Le Dai Hanh, Ward 15, Quận 11</p><h3>Thời gian làm việc</h3><p>Thứ 2 - Thứ 6 (từ 08:00 đến 17:00)</p>',12000000,14000000,1,3,'offline','fulltime','2024-08-18 00:00:00',2,6,'Nhân viên',NULL,79,'2024-06-18 12:44:21','2024-06-18 12:44:21'),(29,4,'Tagging Engineer - Quận 11','<h3>Mô tả công việc</h3><p>- As a Tagging Engineer, you will be responsible for implementing and managing digital analytics tools</p><p>- Understanding and interpreting website traffic metrics, and ensuring the quality of web analytics data.&nbsp;</p><p>- You will collaborate closely with other team members and report performance metrics to senior management.</p><h3>Yêu cầu ứng viên</h3><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Implement and manage digital analytics tools such as GA4, GTM, and Adobe Launch DTM.</li><li>Understand and interpret website traffic metrics including pageviews, sessions, orders placed, and add-to-cart events.</li><li>Apply estimation methodologies and adhere to quality processes.</li><li>Utilize knowledge of analytics and digital marketing to enhance data accuracy and insight generation.</li><li>Use tools like Omnibug for testing web analytics implementations.</li><li>Conduct web-based application testing.</li><li>Apply knowledge of HTML and JavaScript to tagging and analytics tasks.</li><li>Utilize JIRA for task management and defect tracking.</li><li>Manage the defect workflow from identification to closure, ensuring proactive tracking of bugs.</li><li>Test applications independently, ensuring high quality and accuracy of analytics implementations.</li><li>Maintain intermediate-level Excel skills for data analysis and reporting.</li><li>Collaborate daily with team members to ensure seamless workflow and communication.</li><li>Report performance metrics across all domains to senior management.</li></ul><h3>Quyền lợi</h3><p><strong>Required Skillset:</strong></p><p>(1) Necessary to have</p><ul><li>Basic knowledge of digital analytics tools such as GA4, GTM, and Adobe Launch DTM.</li><li>Understanding of website traffic metrics like pageviews, sessions, orders placed, and add-to-cart events.</li><li>Knowledge of estimation methodologies and quality processes.</li><li>Proficiency in analytics and digital marketing concepts.</li><li>Experience in defect workflow management, from identification to closure.</li><li>Excellent communication skills.</li><li>Ability to test applications independently.</li><li>Proactive in tracking bugs raised to closure.</li><li>Experience in collaborating with team members and reporting to senior management.</li></ul><p>(2) Preferred to have</p><ul><li>Experience with tools like Omnibug for testing web analytics.</li><li>Experience in web-based application testing.</li><li>Knowledge of HTML and JavaScript.</li><li>Working knowledge of JIRA.</li><li>Intermediate-level Excel skills.</li></ul><p>Note: Preferred skills are advantageous but not mandatory.</p><h3>Địa điểm làm việc</h3><p>- Hồ Chí Minh: 182 Lê Đại Hành, Quận 11</p><h3>Thời gian làm việc</h3><p>Thứ 2 - Thứ 6 (từ 09:00 đến 18:00)</p><h3>Cách thức ứng tuyển</h3><p>Ứng viên nộp hồ sơ trực tuyến bằng cách bấm&nbsp;<strong>Ứng tuyển</strong>&nbsp;ngay dưới đây.</p><p>Hạn nộp hồ sơ: 27/06/2024</p>',5000000,8000000,1,2,'offline','fulltime','2024-09-18 00:00:00',2,6,'Nhân viên',NULL,79,'2024-06-18 12:46:57','2024-06-18 12:46:57'),(30,4,'Nhân Viên Tư Vấn/ Bán Hàng Qua Điện Thoại/ Telesales / Chăm Sóc Khách Hàng (Sản Phẩm Dinh Dưỡng) - Quận 12','<h3>Mô tả công việc</h3><p>- Gọi ra theo data công ty cung cấp để tư vấn sản phẩm dinh dưỡng cho khách hàng</p><p>- Chăm sóc và giải đáp thắc mắc cho khách hàng cũ và mới</p><p>- Tìm hiểu thêm thông tin khách hàng để tăng doanh số bán hàng</p><p>- Đảm bảo chỉ tiêu theo ngày/ tuần/ tháng</p><h3>Yêu cầu ứng viên</h3><p>- Ưu tiên có kinh nghiệm bán hàng ,tư vấn, telesale.</p><p>- Giọng nói rõ ràng, dễ nghe.</p><p>- Tuổi từ =&lt;32t</p><h3>Quyền lợi</h3><p>MỨC LƯƠNG:</p><p>- Thu nhập TB: 7.000.000 - 12.500.000 VND/tháng.</p><p>- Luơng căn bảng: 5.260.000 VND/tháng.</p><p>- Phụ cấp cơm: 500.000 VND/tháng.</p><p>- Phụ cấp quy trình: 1.200.000 VND/Tháng</p><p>- Thuởng doanh số lên đến 5.500.000 VND/tháng.</p><p>- Thử việc 2 tháng nhận 100% lương</p><p>THỜI GIAN LÀM VIỆC:</p><p>- Từ 8:30 AM – 18:00 PM</p><p>- Off cố định CN hằng tuần (Có tăng ca tuỳ theo tính chất công việc)</p><p>QUYỀN LỢI:</p><p>- Được tham gia BHXH, BHYT đầy đủ.</p><p>- Được tham gia gói b